da8d7ea23c\">안녕하세요, 꾸준한 연구로 최선의 결과를 약속드리는 ‘이수한의원’입니다:)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-0740f3eb-ede2-4b89-b78a-c77ee33b0a4f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a6a73095-e085-4a82-bd73-5a536263e244\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-93716207-4d93-457e-b1f6-700cd90dd852\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-5c3b9f46-39b0-48cb-a23a-e4093bfd0472\">오늘은 이수한의원은 어떤 곳인지 간단히 알려드리려 합니다!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-c4abb665-07b7-465b-9af9-2f95307fb831\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-607228cb-0ee3-418c-a431-a1390b97ef1e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-0a8e8ae4-cab7-4bd4-904b-b2798d8108d1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-7295f58e-236a-43ed-b4a0-fe5732398c35\">진료과목은 크게 6개로 다음과 같이 나누어집니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-3f97a442-26e1-42dd-a46e-03917deb7811\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-552b9d39-b30a-4a2b-a5a4-b7b794684b97\">- 한방부인</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-d13ca029-8875-4a18-8418-d7839aaff0d3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-320ec241-f32a-486a-b42a-a1971551f6fa\">- 한방내과,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-bc1a6bee-adda-4adf-b3d9-fb4abc4096c8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-2b46b406-b0fa-4802-a9c3-49184ee658b9\">- 한방소아과,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-a564af80-5057-497a-9480-0a9392e441bf\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-c0c2ad40-cbd2-4da6-871a-9f9f74498619\">- 추나요법,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-06197462-22d9-4d8e-babd-d617a69138f5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-d1fec1a4-053d-4299-9c70-2ba259d1487e\">- 침치료/약침치료/부항치료</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-a98a05ca-863d-42db-92a6-7775d576c809\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-d6a21c77-d703-4dfe-a951-3c58a90802e7\">- 한약처방 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-975be10e-7f10-4d57-b153-29eb47d1677e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-975be10e-7f10-4d57-b153-29eb47d1677e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/946330348f2eea87.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1080\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/946330348f2eea87.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/946330348f2eea87.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c1694a41-e05f-427d-9eaa-9cf8b6f225f5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-ef2327ed-c1c7-469b-bf4a-f4122b93c0e8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-b62add81-fdf7-4bc3-8dd3-6e809589c827\">이수 한의원은 3인 원장 진료로 이루어지는데요!</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-f2b63a49-73e4-47c8-834d-11924b700734\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-fe6f0e46-4201-4d8e-98a6-a9efc912f4ea\">문학진, 나효석, 이윤호 3명의 한의사가 협진을 통해 환자분께 꼭 필요한 최적의 치료로 최선의 치료결과를 위해 노력합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-67a4cc6e-08b5-4eef-89f8-6eb562755bfc\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cd67fea9-a4cb-4a59-b07a-a192cbfa2a47\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-1d6a8fac-c95e-4eb3-b81e-3fc25e9e7b5c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-161eb000-70f0-4cb8-b436-b817133d1c08\">척추추나교정, 체형추나교정, 난치성 질환, 내과질환, 교통사고 후유증, 부인과, 불</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-04d050a2-f6e7-47d7-92e9-f0c8b8c6efac\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-67f92465-1b92-4146-8763-f5b6e9e3964f\">임과, 성조숙증, 허약아를, 치료합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-78fc3d83-6eea-43c9-85e1-cf9ae66d83eb\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-78fc3d83-6eea-43c9-85e1-cf9ae66d83eb\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b14324b7a8db3057.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1080\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1300\", \"linkUse\" : \"true\", \"link\" : \"https://naver.me/GdJ22wQV\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b14324b7a8db3057.jpg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b14324b7a8db3057.jpg\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"601\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a1e0896a-7c1f-4730-a8bb-e0fc3fd4bc82\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-11c5e8a2-0144-4c0f-905e-d9337edb9ca8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-2e544694-0d4e-4696-a13e-57f03b2e34e3\">한 분 한 분을 위한 맞춤형 진료로 최선의 치료 결과를 약속 드립니다. 이수한의원의 문은 항상 열려 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-3ac9ede0-4083-4950-a768-543987d5b0c0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7c3b8277-7434-4682-bce6-7ad4300eb989\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-11cb871b-ecb7-4cbe-b7f0-f6d0611aeb85\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-ac03590e-04c9-4893-8b6e-b07b3d13d558\">편한 시간에 방문하시면 되며 궁금한 사항은 02-584-1075 로 문의해주세요 :) 감사합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4e12cc59-25d2-4e70-9c52-f0a4a2d92464\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4e12cc59-25d2-4e70-9c52-f0a4a2d92464\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cc0cbcc3c04e3eec.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1800\", \"originalHeight\" : \"800\", \"linkUse\" : \"true\", \"link\" : \"https://naver.me/GdJ22wQV\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cc0cbcc3c04e3eec.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/cc0cbcc3c04e3eec.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"222\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-95dd3106-474b-4140-ad8f-337c5998a556\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"line-height:1.5;\" id=\"SE-a32686b7-d022-45d3-9efd-5ee2f966b706\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system  se-style-unset \" id=\"SE-9e401de4-9bd7-4a1d-b200-c50d7881aedd\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>    </div>",
